For each graph &quot;H&quot; on &quot;h&quot; vertices and each , define
:formula_158
Then each graph &quot;G&quot; on &quot;n&quot; vertices with at most copies of &quot;H&quot; can be made &quot;H&quot;-free by removing at most edges.

