<text>==Events==
*August 23 – Maria Anna Mozart marries Johann Baptist Franz von Berchtold.
*September 24 – The Bolshoi Kamenny Theatre in Saint Petersburg, Russia, opens with a performance of Giovanni Paisiello’s opera &quot;Il mondo della luna&quot;.
*John Broadwood patents a piano pedal in England.

